    "Grilled Lemon-Herb Chicken": `<h2>Grilled Lemon-Herb Chicken</h2><p><strong>Yields:</strong> 50, 100, 150</p><h3>Ingredients</h3><table><thead><tr><th>Ingredient</th><th>50</th><th>100</th><th>150</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Chicken breast, 6 oz portions</td><td>19 lb</td><td>38 lb</td><td>57 lb</td></tr><tr><td>Olive oil</td><td>1.5 qt</td><td>3 qt</td><td>4.5 qt</td></tr><tr><td>Lemon juice</td><td>2 qt</td><td>4 qt</td><td>6 qt</td></tr><tr><td>Garlic, minced</td><td>10 oz</td><td>20 oz</td><td>30 oz</td></tr><tr><td>Parsley and oregano</td><td>2 cups</td><td>4 cups</td><td>6 cups</td></tr><tr><td>Salt and black pepper</td><td>to taste</td><td>to taste</td><td>to taste</td></tr></tbody></table><h3>Method</h3><ol><li><p>Marinate chicken with lemon, garlic, herbs, and oil for at least 2 hours.</p></li><li><p>Grill to 165°F internal temperature.</p></li><li><p>Rest 5 minutes and hold hot for service.</p></li></ol>`,
